data.description: So many possibilities--Large living room, dining room, both bedrooms have great potential and size-- office area connected off first bedroom, (could make a fabulous walk in closet)   the 2nd bedroom has a large setting area  (easy to convert into a 2nd walk in closet or nursery) . Basement family room + 2 bonus rooms, one has windows and one without windows. Double car garage oversized storage.  extra landscaping including a mature tree for extra shade, partially fenced yard. Seller has never used ugs nor well-- they were very weak and did not cover yard when he tested.  basement bath not functional @ this time. Garage door opener is on counter please return to counter when done showing. Lock box has been moved to South door.
